## Implementation Plan

### Design Decisions

**Text Truncation Approach: Option A**
- Justification: Most explicit and widely supported. No vendor prefixes needed. Clear intent.
- Rejected B: `-webkit-line-clamp` requires `-webkit-box` display which can interfere with flexbox layouts
- Rejected C: Removing `max-width` could cause overflow on small screens

**Padding Standardization Strategy**
- Vertical: Standardize to `0.35rem` (most common, used by `.sidebar-item` and `.sidebar-doc-row`)
- Horizontal: Standardize to `0.8rem` (middle ground, used by chapter items and doc rows)
- Rationale: Preserves existing spacing for most elements, minimal visual disruption

### Exact CSS Changes

#### File 1: `toolchain/dress-blueprint-action/assets/common.css`

**Change 1: Line 118 (Light Theme)**
```css
/* BEFORE */
--sidebar-active-bg: var(--sbs-bg-surface);

/* AFTER */
--sidebar-active-bg: var(--sbs-bg-page);
```

**Change 2: Line 314 (Dark Theme)**
```css
/* BEFORE */
--sidebar-active-bg: var(--sbs-bg-surface);

/* AFTER */
--sidebar-active-bg: var(--sbs-bg-page);
```

#### File 2: `toolchain/dress-blueprint-action/assets/blueprint.css`

**Change 3: Line 178 (`.sidebar-item`)**
```css
/* BEFORE */
.sidebar-item {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 0.35rem 0.5rem 0.35rem 0.8rem;
  gap: 0.5rem;
  position: relative;
  cursor: pointer;
  text-decoration: none;
  color: var(--sbs-text-primary);
  max-width: 90%;
  transition: background-color 0.2s ease;
}

/* AFTER */
.sidebar-item {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 0.35rem 0.8rem;
  gap: 0.5rem;
  position: relative;
  cursor: pointer;
  text-decoration: none;
  color: var(--sbs-text-primary);
  white-space: nowrap;
  overflow: hidden;
  text-overflow: ellipsis;
  transition: background-color 0.2s ease;
}
```

Changes:
- Removed `max-width: 90%;`
- Changed `padding: 0.35rem 0.5rem 0.35rem 0.8rem;` to `padding: 0.35rem 0.8rem;`
- Added `white-space: nowrap;`
- Added `overflow: hidden;`
- Added `text-overflow: ellipsis;`

**Change 4: Line 1107 (`.sidebar-chapter-item`)**
```css
/* BEFORE */
.sidebar-chapter-item {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem 0.3rem 1rem;
  gap: 0.5rem;
  position: relative;
  cursor: pointer;
  text-decoration: none;
  color: var(--sbs-text-primary);
  font-weight: 500;
  transition: background-color 0.2s ease;
}

/* AFTER */
.sidebar-chapter-item {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 0.35rem 0.8rem;
  gap: 0.5rem;
  position: relative;
  cursor: pointer;
  text-decoration: none;
  color: var(--sbs-text-primary);
  font-weight: 500;
  white-space: nowrap;
  overflow: hidden;
  text-overflow: ellipsis;
  transition: background-color 0.2s ease;
}
```

Changes:
- Changed `padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem 0.3rem 1rem;` to `padding: 0.35rem 0.8rem;`
- Added `white-space: nowrap;`
- Added `overflow: hidden;`
- Added `text-overflow: ellipsis;`

**Change 5: `.sidebar-doc-row` (if exists near line 1107)**
```css
/* BEFORE (likely) */
